OL,3,CKent MP calls for #22m South East
OL,4,CWater fine to be waived to force
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FA proposed #22m fine for South East
OL,8,FWater should be waived, the Tunbridge
OL,9,FWells MP has proposed.
OL,11,FMike Martin has suggested the proposed
OL,12,Fpenalty for repeated supply failures
OL,13,Fis replaced by a compulsory investment
OL,14,Fplan instead.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
