PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774383073
OL,3,CKent MP calls for #22m South East
OL,4,CWater fine to be waived to force
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FMike Martin said: "This fine isn't
OL,8,Fjustice. It's a paltry figure that
OL,9,Ffails to reflect the true cost of
OL,10,Fongoing water outages on our local
OL,11,Fresidents and businesses.
OL,13,F"My constituents don't want endless
OL,14,Ffines for a water company that isn't
OL,15,Finterested in changing its behaviour
OL,16,Fand hasn't learned lessons from the
OL,17,Fpast.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
