PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1774383073
OL,3,CKent MP calls for #22m South East
OL,4,CWater fine to be waived to force
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,F"They want the plentiful and safe
OL,8,Fsupply of water that they pay for. My
OL,9,Fwater resilience plan will actually
OL,10,Fdeliver this."
OL,12,FThe Ofwat fine was proposed on 5 March
OL,13,Fand related to multiple supply
OL,14,Finterruptions in Kent and Sussex
OL,15,Fbetween 2020 and 2023.
OL,17,FThe regulator has separately opened an
OL,18,Finvestigation into sustained outages
OL,19,Fin Kent and Sussex in December 2025
OL,20,Fand January 2026.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]
