OL,3,CKent MP calls for #22m South East
OL,4,CWater fine to be waived to force
OL,5,Cinvestment
OL,7,FAt the height of the incident, South
OL,8,FEast Water reported that 30,000
OL,9,Fcustomers across the two counties were
OL,10,Fwithout water, or experiencing low
OL,11,Fwater pressure.
OL,13,FA South East Water spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"We are carefully considering the
OL,15,Fdetail of Ofwat's draft decision
OL,16,Fpublished on 5 March and will be
OL,17,Fproviding our detailed response within
OL,18,Fthe consultation period."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
